SIZE=(16,67), ORIENT=(02,07)
WINDOW BOX
EASEL ON


                       Balance Order - Help

    Option that is used to decide how the balance amount is used
    to determine the rate.  Valid values are:

    GE  Rate is used if balance is greater than or equal to the
        calculated combined balance or the individual balance
        of the account. (Default)
    LE  Rate is used if balance is less than or equal to the
        calculated combined balance or the individual
        balance of the account.
                                                                _
    F12=Cancel                                            M03015S

EASEL OFF
LABEL=(LABEL,IMPORTANT)
FIELD=PFKEY,    PIC='X(01)', ATTR=(DISPLAY,HIDDEN)
LABEL=(LABEL,IMPORTANT)
